{
  "stem": "3994.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that, we went back to Gyor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at that time, already started with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was working, did my [INAUDIBLE] millinery, he worked in a very big shop where he was a manager.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went with different things there, all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we met there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from then on, we were meeting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what is--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a real gentleman, tall, with glasses, [INAUDIBLE], and a very nice gentleman, all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'41.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In December on the 7th, 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nearly 19.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My fam-- in Hungary, also, in the same city everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody in the same city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working then what I learned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after, when we wanted to establish ourselves, they were all content to go and come to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he had to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But is-- it wasn't the real army, where they put the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was more the working army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There they put them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wedding?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in '41, it was already the war everywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't have a white wedding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a very nice wedding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had about 100 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had ?] my wedding, with my family and all the friends and my parents' friends, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were very happy together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were already very hard times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when they took my husband away--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in end of '42 .",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in '39, we went to-- I have already been in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in '40, well, everybody was afraid, because Hungary and Germany-- I mean, Austria and Germany was all on the border.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody felt the war is here, and they will come.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
